valvoline inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Materials
Industry: Chemicals
Sub-Industry: Specialty Chemicals
Valvoline, Inc. manufactures and distributes automotive lubricants and chemicals. The Company produces motor oil, antifreeze, brake fluid, and grease products. Valvoline serves customers worldwide.




